                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Sleeper</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-08-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 24, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Sleeper states that the insurgents are in possession of the towns of San
                    Juan y Martinez and San Luis, Province of Pinar Del Rio. He says they have
                    threatened to blow up bridges and burn property of Western Railway (English) if
                    company continues to transport government troops.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
